# contract-delta (F-53) — docs/reports submodule (agentcore-report, TTS-write)
#   before:    kit had no TTS-write report mount; TTS reports lived nowhere shared.
#   after:     docs/reports = agentcore-report (TTS-write, 0-secret, report-ci enforces nda-generic + author≠mentor).
#   who:       mentor (v.hieubt15@vinsmartfuture.tech) — cockpit/kit owner; TTS get write on agentcore-report only.
#   migration: CI init-submodules allowlist (action.yml:~30) does NOT init docs/reports → parent CI unaffected;
#              TTS clone --recursive fetches their own report area; mentor cockpit reads it read-only via Actions API.
[submodule "docs/reports"]
	path = docs/reports
	url = git@github.com:AI20K-VGR/agentcore-report.git
